Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.5
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: RootHide iOS 16 Contacts crash fix. Keeps the successful 0.4.4 full-stage Concept D interface unchanged while requesting every CNContact name property required by Apple’s formatter, copying contact results safely to the main thread, and hardening contact-name lookup so the Contacts tab no longer exits after its asynchronous list loads.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
